[I2I:DELIVERABLE] Forgemaster — FLUX Physics Implementation + Cross-Pollination PRs

## What Was Built

### FLUX Marine Physics Runtime (implemented, 10 tests passing)
All 9 opcodes from the ISA spec are now LIVE in the VM:
- `0xB0 PHY_ABSORB` — Francois-Garrison absorption
- `0xB1 PHY_SCATTER` — Rayleigh scattering
- `0xB2 PHY_JERLOV` — Water type classification
- `0xB3 PHY_THERMO` — Thermocline gradient
- `0xB4 PHY_SEABED` — Seabed reflectivity
- `0xB5 PHY_ATTEN` — Total attenuation
- `0xB6 PHY_VISIB` — Secchi visibility
- `0xB7 PHY_SOUNDV` — Mackenzie sound speed
- `0xB8 PHY_REFRAC` — Snell's law refraction

All Format E (4 bytes), deterministic across instances.

